[{"id":"VH969679","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH969672.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">In lines 1-2 (<span class=\"non-base_language\">Petis</span> . . . <span class=\"non-base_language\">possis</span>), we learn that Tacitus wanted Pliny to help him write</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH969679_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\">\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"poetry style:1\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<p class=\"title_line passage-title\">Pliny writes to Tacitus about the eruption of Mt. Vesuvius.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">1&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Petis ut tibi avunculi mei exitum scribam, quo verius</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>tradere posteris possis. Gratias ago; nam video morti</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>eius si celebretur a te immortalem gloriam esse</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>propositam. Quamvis enim pulcherrimarum clade</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">5&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>terrarum, ut populi ut urbes memorabili casu, quasi</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>semper victurus occiderit, quamvis ipse plurima</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>opera et mansura condiderit, multum tamen</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>perpetuitati eius scriptorum tuorum aeternitas addet.</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Equidem beatos puto quibus deorum munere datum</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">10&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>est aut facere scribenda aut scribere legenda,</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>beatissimos vero quibus utrumque. Horum in numero</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>avunculus meus et suis libris et tuis erit. Quo libentius</span><br />\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>suscipio, deposco etiam quod iniungis.</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">a eulogy for his uncle</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">a letter of condolence to his uncle’s widow</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">a more accurate account his uncle’s demise</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">a complete biography of his uncle</p>"],"answer":2}]